- `?compromise-followup`: `--` (was live) — matched pre-committed refutation shape: zero 5501/5715 events from 203.0.113.45 in the 10-min forward window. Extended check also clear: zero successful auth from 203.0.113.45 to any host in the full 40-min window. Trust root reached (v-001 is an external endpoint; no upstream forensics accessible).

